name: community-help
topic:
This channel is for getting help from other community members with your questions about using Claude.

For official help with your Claude account, please go to https://support.anthropic.com/.

***Note***:  Discord moderators **cannot** access your account or provide official support here.

name: share-your-project
topic: This channel is for sharing your projects using Claude. Please do not posts links to projects that have nothing to do with Anthropic services.

name: 430-discord-feedback-chat
topic: Chat w/high-presence community members RE: incoming Discord changes for feedback, suggestions, etc.

name: api-help
topic: **Hey! We’re here to help you build with the Claude API. Post your question below and we’ll come back to you as soon as possible!**

name: featured-projects
topic: Projects featured here have been selected by our staff and then won, by community vote, the Project of the Month or Project of the Year.  Please see the pinned message(s) in #share-your-project for contest rules & requirements.

name: feedback
topic: **Hey! Have an idea for a new or improved feature?  Experiencing some strange behavior you can't explain?  Ideas for this community?  We’re all ears!  Create a positive, constructive post with feedback on any of the taggable subjects, along with screenshots where applicable, we will share it with the relevant team members here at Anthropic.**

name: model-changes
topic:
For reporting suspect model changes/regressions. Please post details! That means share your prompt, the results before the change, AND the results after the change. Have others test your prompt, and their own similar prompt to see if they get the same result.
"Model changed, Claude bad now," is not actionable feedback!

name: project-history
topic: We’d love to see and celebrate how you're building with the Claude API. Show us your projects by posting below!

name: prompt-directory
topic: Use this channel to share your favorite prompts, brainstorm new ideas, and seek advice from other builders and AI enthusiasts.

name: prompt-discussion
topic: Use this channel to share your favorite prompts, brainstorm new ideas, and seek advice from other builders and AI enthusiasts.

name: ❓question-of-the-week
topic: The "Question of the Week" is a great way to get to know your fellow community members, and stimulate engaging, meaningful conversation.  When responding, please keep your response brief, but as long as you need to answer completely. Please keep your responses to ONE message, but feel free to comment on others' responses.  And as always, stay positive, constructive, and relatively safe for work.

name: ❓qotw-repo
topic:
For Staff Members to submit their ideas for the Question of the Week.
We will pull from this channel every Monday to post in the #:question:question-of-the-week channel.  Please use searching to see if the question is already here or already used.  We will delete and re-add the questions we use, adding a strikethrough to the text to keep track.

name: responsible-deployment
topic: Safety is core to Anthropic’s mission and we’re committed to building an ecosystem where users can safely interact with and build on top of our products in a helpful, honest and harmless way. You’ve received API access because you share our commitment to working towards responsible AI deployment. Our #responsible-deployment channel is a space for builders to share tips on staying safe, and to ensure that their applications adhere to our acceptable use policy (AUP).

name: support
topic: Our Discord community is a great place to ask questions and collaborate with other Anthropic AI users and developers from around the world.  However, Discord is NOT a way to interface with Anthropic's Support Team.  Please familiarize yourself with the information below to find out where and how to get the help you need with Claude, the Anthropic API, or with your account.
